#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><div><p>
#: template.html:37
msgid ""
"This release features many improvements in all areas, including a completely "
"revamped interface, a new multiplayer faction, dozens of new portraits, "
"updated unit animations, hundreds of bug fixes, and a vastly improved map "
"editor. Try out the new features for yourself, or read on for more details..."
msgstr ""

